quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,67,"Ko Kanko tagiri ben mon Aadam, immorde e mbulmbulndi, refti O tagiri on …ìaawo …óum, e to…ì…ìere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere ∆¥ii∆¥am, refti …ìaawo …óum, O yaltiniri on e deedi neeniraa…ìe mon …ìen, entoy tokosoy, fii no yottoron cukaaku ngun, mawnon haa wonton nayee…ìe, - kono hara wo…ó…ìe e mo'on, maayay ado …óum, - haa no yottoron dumunna happaa…óo ka Allah, mo …óuytotaako …ìeydotaako, belajo'o, ka nafitoron …óii hujjaaji fii anndugol kattal e gootaagu Allah ngun."
  40,68,"Ko Kanko Allah tun, woni wuurnoowo, e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: "wonu", o wona."
  40,69,"A tinaali, an Nulaa…óo, …ìen wennjondirtee…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, fennoo…ìe …óe, e hoore ko …óe fee√±i kon? a ≈ãal…óay e ma…ì…ìe, e ko …ìe …óuurnotoo e goonga kon, hoore ko ka fee√±i kon."
  40,70,"∆Åen fennu…ìe Alqur'aana, e ko Men immindini kon e Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, immorde e goonga, aray ka …ìen fennoo…ìe annda, battane e bone mun."
  40,71,"∆Åe anndoyay battane fennugol ma…ì…ìe ngol, tuma nde kolmboyaa ka daa…óe ma…ì…ìe, …ìe jolkiree ka koy…óe, halfinaa…ìe lepte …óen daasa …ìe."
  40,72,"∆Åe ndaasee e ndiyam wul…óam haa fati, refti …ìe hu…ì…ìee Yiite ngen."
  40,73,"Refti …ìe feliree wi'aneede: ko honto woni rewetee…ói mon, …ói aa∆¥ino…óon wonnde on sirkiranii…ói dewal?"
  40,74,"Ko honto …óin sanamuuji, …ói rewayno…óon, hara wanaa Allah, …ói nafataa …ói lorrataa? Heefer…ìe …ìen jaaboo: ∆äi majjitorike men. Wurin, men wonaano aduna, e rewugol ko hanndunoo e reweede. Ko wano …ìee …óoo majjiri non, Allah majjinirta yeddu…ìe goonga …ìen, e kala nokku e jamaanu."
  40,75,"∆Åe wi'anee : ko fawi on …óee lepte, ko sabu ko weltorayno…óon kon, sirku on, e ko wewlayno…óon kon fantinon."
  40,76,"Natiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton poomaa. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde townitanii…ìe goonga …ìen."
  40,77,"Mu√±√±o, an Nulaa…óo, e ko yim…ìe maa lorrete …ìe fenne kon. Pellet, ko Allah fodu maa wallude kon, ko goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Ko si Men holle yoga e ko Men kammbirani …ìe kon e lepte, e nguurndam maa, wano fe∆¥∆¥irnoo ka hare Badri, maa hara Men ∆¥ettite ado mun, fow e mun, ko ka Amen tun, woni ruttorde ma…ì…ìe, √ëalnde Darngal, Men yo…ìa …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, Men naatna…ìe ka Yiite, …ìe lutta ton poomaa."